(252, 2, '2013-08-01 13:24:40', '2013-08-01 13:24:40', '<div class="video-container"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/6_39aH16qRU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\nHas your school signed on to partner with Families That Can? Our mission is to educate, empower and mobilize charter school families from across the state. One way we do that is by offering free parent workshops on a wide variety of topics.\n"We help activate and engage parents to be advocates for their schools and all schools," says Valieria Koss, a former charter school teacher who now works with charter school parents from across San Diego, Orange County and the Inland Empire.\n- [Find out more about how Families That Can can help engage your parents to support your school!](/2011/03/how-families-that-can-supports-schools.html)\n- [Email the Families That Can representative in your region to set up a free workshop today!](/contact.html)\n', 'Video: Bring Free Parent Advocacy Workshops to Your School', 'We want to partner with you - get in touch today so we can offer a free workshop for parents at your school!\n', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'video_bring_free_parent_advocacy_workshops_to_your_school', '', '', '2013-08-01 13:24:40', '2013-08-01 13:24:40', '', 0, 'http://192.168.20.50/wp/?p=252', 0, 'post', '', 0),
