(509, 1, '2015-12-14 21:55:16', '2015-12-14 21:55:16', '<p>Shawn Brown is our Director, Parent Organizing, Northern California. He manages our team of parent organizers in Sacramento, San Juan, Oakland, Richmond and San Jose. Shawn was the Campaign Director at Voices for Youth in Chicago, and has extensive organizing experience at SEIU and ACLU and other organizations across the Midwest</p>\n', 'Shawn Brown', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'staff-member', '', '', '2016-01-19 22:16:17', '2016-01-19 22:16:17', '', 412, 'http://192.168.20.50/wp/?page_id=509', 0, 'page', '', 0),
