(947, 3, '2016-01-13 04:22:13', '2016-01-13 04:22:13', '<div class="figure embedded-image none"><img alt="Great Schools Logo (Entry/Page Lead Image)" src="/assets_c/2013/09/Screen Shot 2013-09-26 at 10.48.01 AM-cropped-proto-ftc_theme___lead.jpg" width="612" height="269" class="mt-image-none" style="" /></div>\n\n<p>GreatSchools is a website that provides useful information for parents on all kinds of schools in their neighborhood - district and charter public schools, as well as private schools. Each school profile also includes reviews written by parents. What are parents writing about your school? Find out and contribute your own review and your school will be entered in a $5,000 sweepstakes.\nTell parents to write reviews about your school at <a href="http://www.greatschools.org/sweepstakes">www.greatschools.org/sweepstakes</a>.\nReviews are anonymous and just take a moment to write. Parents, teachers and students 13 and older in K-12 schools can write reviews.  Reviews are a great way to let people know what\'s happening at your school beyond the test scores.\nWhen your school receives 3 new reviews this month, it\'s entered in the drawing for $5,000!\nIncrease your school\'s chances to win.  Every review over 3 per month gives your school another entry into the drawing - up to 10 entries each month.\nFind materials to promote the sweepstakes, like sample emails, newsletter inserts and flyers for parents, at <a href="www.greatschools.org/promote">www.greatschools.org/promote</a>.\n<a href="www.greatschools.org/sweepstakes">Read the Official Rules</a>.</p>\n', 'Write a Review and Your School Could Win $5,000', 'Write a review of your school on GreatSchools and your school will be entered in a drawing this October. Learn more and find resources to spread the word to other parents at your school.\n', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '255-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-13 04:22:13', '2016-01-13 04:22:13', '', 255, 'http://dev.ccsafamilies.org/255-revision-v1/', 0