(1030, 3, '2016-01-13 04:24:37', '2016-01-13 04:24:37', '<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AIFzncWHcFc"><img src="http://www.ccsa.org/icon-rocketship-video-02.png" align="right"></a>Check out this great new video from San Jose charter Rocketship Los Sue√±os Academy, which has developed a strong, inclusive program for all students. As part of their collaborative approach, special education and general education teachers work together in a co-teaching model to support the needs of all students. Watch the video:\n<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AIFzncWHcFc">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AIFzncWHcFc</a></p>\n', 'Success Teaching Students with Special Needs', 'Watch this video about how a San Jose charter school helps all students grow together\n', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '325-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-13 04:24:37', '2016-01-13 04:24:37', '', 325, 'http://dev.ccsafamilies.org/325-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
